'''印第安納印第安納波利斯聖殿'''（Indianapolis Indiana Temple）是位於[[印第安納波利斯|印第安納波利斯]]北郊[[卡梅爾_(印第安納州)|卡梅爾]]的一座[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]的聖殿<ref>{{citation |first= Rachel |last= Sterzer |date= January 29, 2011 |title= Indiana temple to be built in Indianapolis area |url= http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/60417/Indiana-temple-to-be-built-in-Indianapolis-area.html |newspaper= [[Church_News|Church News]] |accessdate= 2012-11-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140515073711/http://www.ldschurchnewsarchive.com/articles/60417/Indiana-temple-to-be-built-in-Indianapolis-area.html |archive-date= 2014-05-15 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。印第安納印第安納波利斯聖殿的建設計劃在2010年10月2日公佈<ref name="Taylor 2010-10-02">{{citation |first= Scott |last= Taylor |title= President Thomas S. Monson opens conference by announcing 5 new temples |url= http://www.deseretnews.com/article/700070415/President-Thomas-S-Monson-opens-Mormon-conference-by-announcing-5-new-temples.html |newspaper= [[Deseret_News|Deseret News]] |date= October 2, 2010 |accessdate= 2012-11-11 |archive-date= 2018-12-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20181211060426/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/700070415/President-Thomas-S-Monson-opens-Mormon-conference-by-announcing-5-new-temples.html |dead-url= no }}.</ref><ref>{{citation |url= http://www.mormonnewsroom.org/article/news-five-new-temples-october-2010-Monson |contribution= Five New Temples Announced |date= October 2, 2010 |title= News Release |work= Newsroom |publisher= LDS Church |accessdate= 2012-11-11 |archive-date= 2019-04-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190401180045/https://www.mormonnewsroom.org/article/news-five-new-temples-october-2010-Monson |dead-url= no }}</ref>，外觀類似[[亞利桑那吉拉谷聖殿|亞利桑那吉拉谷聖殿]]<ref>{{citation |first= Sarah Jane |last= Weaver |date= August 23, 2015 |title= President Eyring dedicates first temple in the Hoosier State |url= http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865635180/President-Eyring-dedicates-first-temple-in-the-Hoosier-State.html |newspaper= [[Deseret_News|Deseret News]] |accessdate= 2016-04-21 |archive-date= 2016-10-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161022065024/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/865635180/President-Eyring-dedicates-first-temple-in-the-Hoosier-State.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2012年9月29日，聖殿舉行了動工儀式<ref>{{citation |first= Michael |last= Boren |date= September 29, 2012 |title= Mormons celebrate groundbreaking for new temple in Carmel |url= http://www.indystar.com/article/20120929/local0101/120929006/Mormons-celebrate-groundbreaking-new-temple-Carmel |newspaper= [[The_Indianapolis_Star|The Indianapolis Star]] |accessdate= 2012-11-11 |archive-date= 2015-10-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151021180719/http://www.indystar.com/article/20120929/local0101/120929006/Mormons-celebrate-groundbreaking-new-temple-Carmel |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{citation |title= Mormon Temple being built in Carmel |url= http://www.wishtv.com/dpp/news/local/hamilton_county/mormon-temple-being-built-in-carmel |publisher= [[WISH-TV|WISH-TV]] |location= Indianapolis, Indiana |accessdate= 2012-11-11 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121102065224/http://www.wishtv.com/dpp/news/local/hamilton_county/mormon-temple-being-built-in-carmel |archivedate= 2012-11-02 }}</ref><ref>{{citation |first= Joseph |last= Walker |date= September 30, 2012 |title= Ground broken for LDS temple in Indiana |url= http://www.deseretnews.com/article/765608255/Ground-broken-for-LDS-temple-in-Indiana.html?pg=all |newspaper= [[Deseret_News|Deseret News]] |accessdate= 2012-11-11 |archive-date= 2017-09-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170910130153/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/765608255/Ground-broken-for-LDS-temple-in-Indiana.html?pg=all |dead-url= no }}</ref>。聖殿在2015年7月17日至8月8日之間對公眾開放，在2015年8月23日奉獻。

